-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/copper-rises-as-europe-debt-crisis-concerns-abate-lme-preview.html
Copper climbed for a second day
after the  European Central Bank  and international policy makers
coordinated to lend dollars to banks to help tame the credit
crisis, boosting demand prospects for industrial metals.  Market News:  Metals News:  
